╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

PROXY CHECKER FULL — is a professional proxy testing and management tool 
for Windows. Features high-speed multithreaded checking, proxy type detection 
(HTTP/HTTPS/SOCKS4/SOCKS5), geolocation lookup, anonymity level analysis, 
and export functionality. Perfect for security researchers and privacy enthusiasts.

